===message:I believe I would also be a Antifederalist.  Yes, the Federalist proposed a checks and balance system but like you stated how do we know if it would have worked.  Like the Antifederalist I do not think and even division of power could be achied between the national and state government leaving lower and middle class with the short end of the stick.
